*        fileinfo.spt - Produce information about a file
*        This program counts the number of characters and lines in a file.

         &TRIM    =  1
NEXTL    CHARS    =  CHARS + SIZE(INPUT)                    :F(DONE)
         LINES    =  LINES + 1                              :(NEXTL)
DONE     OUTPUT   =  CHARS ' characters, ' +LINES ' lines read'
END
